metadata.description:
When I first met Steven Bartlett, I saw something very familiar  a younger version of myself.

Driven. Intense. Hyper-effective. But also, deeply introspective.

Two years later, he asked me: What have you changed your mind about since our last conversation? And honestly, he made me pause.

In this clip, I share how Steven became an unexpected mirror.
How I went from running 17 full-time roles to slowly stepping back.
Not because I lost ambition  but because I found clarity.

What part of yourself do you recognize in others?

#MoGawdat #StevenBartlett #SelfDiscovery #Leadership #PersonalGrowth #1BillionHappy #Reflection #MindsetShift #SlowDownToGrow #BurnoutRecovery #Introspection #ModernWisdom
